<li><i>The Tales of Henry James</i> by <a href="/wiki/Edward_Wagenknecht" title="Edward Wagenknecht">Edward Wagenknecht</a> (New York: Frederick Ungar Publishing Co. 1984) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/080442957X" class="internal">ISBN 0-8044-2957-X</a></li>
</ul>
